rustdesk-hbbs (1.1.14-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add --ip option to force IPv4-only or IPv6-only binding
  * Add --bind-addr option to bind to specific IP address
  * Fix IPv6-only binding issue on some systems
  * Enhanced network binding logging

